     Created: 2026-03-06
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Visual Studio 2022 Dark theme. Pixel-accurate
         reproduction of the VS2022 color palette: #1E1E1E background, #252526 panels,
         #0078D4 accent, and #D4D4D4 foreground.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in VS2022DarkTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

